"function":"evaluate_two_sum",
"mode":"conceptual",
"match":"exact",
"signature":"def evaluate_two_sum():",
"prompt":"Evaluate the time and space complexity of your two-pointer two_sum\nsolution. Then evaluate this alternative:\n\n    def two_sum(nums, target):\n        prev_map = {}\n        for i in range(len(nums)):\n            diff = target - nums[i]\n            if diff in prev_map:\n                return [prev_map[diff], i]\n            prev_map[nums[i]] = i\n\nWhich has better time complexity?\nWhich has better space complexity?"
},
